{"bookId":"26785317","title":"秋水堂论金瓶梅","author":"田晓菲","cover":"https://wfqqreader-1252317822.image.myqcloud.com/cover/317/26785317/s_26785317.jpg","version":996424159,"format":"epub","type":0,"price":32.99,"originalPrice":0,"soldout":0,"bookStatus":1,"payType":4097,"finished":1,"maxFreeChapter":33,"free":0,"mcardDiscount":0,"ispub":1,"cpid":2000001048,"centPrice":3299,"category":"文学榜-文学鉴赏","hasLecture":1,"intro":"“云霞满纸”，袁宏道在写给董其昌的信里，这样称道《金瓶梅》。《金瓶梅》问世四百余年来，得到无数作家、学者的宝爱和传抄，从李渔、曹雪芹，到胡适、张爱玲……无不从《金瓶梅》中汲取营养。《金瓶梅》不仅仅是一部闺房私情之书，更是一部深微体察人性的“罪与罚”之书：书中所有人物都沉沦于欲望的苦海，被贪欲、嗔怒、嫉妒、痴情的巨浪所抛掷。《金瓶梅》作者之如椽巨笔，直入人性深不可测的部分，揭示人心的复杂而又毫无伤感与滥情；一个读者必须有健壮的脾胃，健全的精神，成熟的头脑，才能够真正欣赏与理解《金瓶梅》，直面其中因为极端写实而格外惊心动魄的暴力。","lastChapterIdx":112,"paperBook":{"skuId":"12563070"},"chapterSize":112,"updateTime":1605630324,"onTime":1574059826,"unitPrice":0.05,"marketType":0,"isbn":"9787559815347","publisher":"广西师范大学出版社","publishTime":"2019-03-01 00:00:00","totalWords":258608,"publishPrice":89.00,"bookSize":998591,"recommended":0,"lectureRecommended":0,"follow":0,"secret":0,"offline":0,"lectureOffline":0,"finishReading":0,"isAutoPay":0,"availables":0,"paid":0,"isChapterPaid":0,"showLectureButton":1,"wxtts":1,"star":85,"ratingCount":1053,"ratingDetail":{"one":28,"two":13,"three":72,"four":212,"five":727,"recent":13},"newRating":775,"newRatingCount":884,"newRatingDetail":{"good":685,"fair":175,"poor":24,"recent":13,"myRating":"","title":"值得一读"},"copyrightInfo":{"id":2000001048,"name":"理想国imaginist","userVid":383823679},"authorSeg":[{"words":"田晓菲","highlight":1}]}